    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186570/extras/202daa53370987c5a159a5f47d0c9ed2.avif?t=1745685526\" width=800 height=182 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186570/extras/487fb47aacdf9223086855d317905a0e.webp?t=1745685526\" width=616 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186570/extras/3866d81c660cddcead8cc24325efd219.poster.avif?t=1745685526\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186570/extras/3866d81c660cddcead8cc24325efd219.webm?t=1745685526\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186570/extras/3866d81c660cddcead8cc24325efd219.mp4?t=1745685526\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186570/extras/9362ec34af4871c5a1604005954e95fc.webp?t=1745685526\" width=616 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >记者沃尔特-马丁斯在 &quot;TELEFORUM &quot;的广播中结束了自己的生命，这是一个现已被取消的电视节目。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你正在访问他的遗孀的公寓--安慰这个悲伤的女人，并对这个可怕的故事给予一些启示...... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但这并不是你来这里的主要原因。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这都是为了那盘磁带，不是吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186570/extras/f36047b2e7e88aba59413be206473b42.poster.avif?t=1745685526\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186570/extras/f36047b2e7e88aba59413be206473b42.webm?t=1745685526\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186570/extras/f36047b2e7e88aba59413be206473b42.mp4?t=1745685526\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >尝试找出真相，而且，请■■不要■■■■■ ■■■■ ■■■■。这很重要。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特点</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >模拟VHS的视觉风格，灵感来自发现的恐怖片；</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为记者，对一位悲伤的妻子进行采访--在寻找答案和把她推到边缘之间取得平衡；</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为摄像师，探索周围的环境，揭开真相；</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多重结局--你能解开磁带之谜吗？</p></li></ul>",
